name: ParaSHOOT (dsert)
description:
A one-minute long game about saving your life at very high altitudes. Can you open your parachute in time?

This game used sound effects from freesound.org (NenadSimic, complex_waveform, Benboncan, Baltiyar13, nextmaking, qubodup, Huggy13ear and magedu). All other assets and programming by me.
